milk tree
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:also called milkwood, turepo a native forest tree with milky sap. <i>Paratrophis microphylla<i> (formerly <i>P. heterophylla</i> (Laing and Blackwell)), and <i>Epicarpus microphyllus </i>(Morris)
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
